            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1ab096c671befd594e22708a02babcbeef">
                <title>static get_current_page ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Try to get page from Director and if in CMS then get it from CMS page, fallback to <link linkend="d6/d68/class_modular_1_1_controller">Controller</link> url via page_for_path.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>|| </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
